A postcard of the painting _The New Car_ by English children's author and illustrator Angus Clifford Racey Helps (1913-1971).

This postcard was published in England by the Medici Society in the 1960s or 1970s. It is 3½ x 5½ inch (9x14cm) size. It is unused and in Mint condition.
